items.title: Denmark bans all civilian drone flights ahead of European summit
items.description: Denmark is one of several European countries that have reported "drone incidents" in recent weeks.

items.title: Moldova's pro-EU party wins vote mired in claims of Russian interference
items.description: The election was seen as critical for Moldova's EU path, and President Maia Sandu warned the country's future was in danger.

items.title: The Indian superstar whose political rally turned fatal for dozens
items.description: At least 40 people died over the weekend in a crowd crush at a political rally organised by Vijay's party.

items.title: Singapore denies entry to exiled HK pro-democracy activist
items.description: Nathan Law's presence "would not be in national interests", Singapore authorities say.

items.title: Death toll rises to four after Michigan church shooting and arson attack
items.description: The attacker drove a vehicle into the church during a service and opened fire, before being killed himself.
